Squizzy::

She screamed again as her body started to burn.  She bit down again 
on Arcangel's hand and struggled, "LET ME GO!" She then remembered 
ehr crossbow, but it was unloaded.  She cursed under her breath and 
bit down on his hand again. "LET ME...AHHHH!" as the burning became 
more intense, so did the pain.
